   576                              <1> ; ============================================================================
   577                              <1> ; SSE2 Non-Temporal Flip: back buffer -> framebuffer (VRAM)
   578                              <1> ; Uses MOVNTDQ to bypass CPU cache - massive speedup for VRAM writes
   579                              <1> ; ============================================================================
