   536                              <1> ; ============================================================================
   537                              <1> ; xhci_reset - Reset the XHCI controller
   538                              <1> ; Returns: EAX = 1 on success, 0 on timeout
   539                              <1> ; Uses PIT-based timeouts so they work on any CPU speed.
   540                              <1> ; ============================================================================
